":"agent:main:cron:3709e1d2-67b1-4eff-92e4-b586ec802978","kind":"other","channel":"webchat","label":"Cron: 空闲检测自主学习","displayName":"webchat:g-agent-main-cron-3709e1d2-67b1-4eff-92e4-b586ec802978","deliveryContext":{"channel":"webchat"},"updatedAt":1774639129607,"sessionId":"8e5a8fb4-4501-4dee-b729-126e179aa770","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":48710,"systemSent":true,"abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"webchat","transcriptPath":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/agents/main/sessions/8e5a8fb4-4501-4dee-b729-126e179aa770.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"This is a cron job task asking me to check for active sessions and if none exist, perform autonomous learning about relevant industries. Let me check the sessions_list first."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_sa1opdp5yjuk_1","name":"sessions_list","arguments":{"activeMinutes":5,"messageLimit":1}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774639130113}]}]},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774639133878}}
{"type":"message","id":"6c775499","parentId":"502cd8c3","timestamp":"2026-03-27T19:18:57.322Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Only one session found is the current cron job session itself. There's no other active user conversation in the last 5 minutes. The current session is just this cron job checking itself. So there are no active user conversations.\n\nI should perform the autonomous learning task:\n1. Search for latest news on 企业数字化转型、智能安防、网络系统集成、IT运维服务\n2. Organize 3-5 key pieces of information\n3. Save to /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/memory/学习笔记.md\n\nLet me first read the miaoda-web-search skill to understand how to perform web searches.","thinkingSignature":"2951f98ab156d43f1a40b478561a46a11b3c8a0be41a3fef981ba7d028bfc0ac"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_6v2bhqo6avo6_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/skills/miaoda-web-search/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":853,"output":166,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45000,"cost":{"input":0.0002559,"output":0.0001992,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0017745299999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774639133881}}
{"type":"message","id":"3da27ea0","parentId":"6c775499","timestamp":"2026-03-27T19:18:57.328Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_6v2bhqo6avo6_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\r\nname: miaoda-web-search\r\ndescription: \"ALWAYS use this skill FIRST when you need to find, look up, or verify ANY information from the internet — do NOT guess URLs and fetch them directly. Provides necessary command usage instructions for keyword-based web search with AI-generated summaries. 触发词：搜索, 网页搜索, 搜一下, 查一下, 查询, 了解, 找一下, 帮我看看, web search, look up, find out, search, 搜索摘要, 查资料, 搜索引擎, 最新信息, 最近动态\"\r\noverride-tools:\r\n  - web_search\r\n---\r\n\r\n# Web Search\r\n\r\n通过 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary` 按关键词搜索互联网信息，由 AI 自动总结。\r\n\r\n## Quick Reference\r\n\r\n| 参数 | 说明 | 必需 | 默认值 |\r\n|------|------|------|--------|\r\n| `--query` | 搜索关键词（1-500 字符） | 是 | - |\r\n| `--output, -o` | 输出格式: text/json | 否 | text |\r\n\r\n## 命令选择决策树\r\n\r\n```\r\n用户想获取互联网信息\r\n├─ 有具体 URL → miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n├─ 无具体 URL，需搜索 → miaoda-studio-cli search-summary\r\n└─ 先搜索再深入 → search-summary 获取 URL → web-crawl 提取详情（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n```\r\n\r\n## 使用示例\r\n\r\n```bash\r\n# 按关键词搜索\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"React 19 新特性\"\r\n\r\n# 搜索并获取 JSON 输出\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"ByteDance 开源项目\" --output json\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Common Mistakes\r\n\r\n| 错误 | 正确做法 |\r\n|------|----------|\r\n| 无具体 URL 时用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl` | 无 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary`，有 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl`（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill） |\r\n| 搜索关键词超过 500 字符 | 提炼核心关键词，保持精简 |\r\n| 需要后续程序处理结果但未加 `--output json` | 需要解析结果时始终加 `--output json` |\r\n| 命令失败后不检查退出码 | 退出码 `1` 表示失败，检查参数和网络后重试 |\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774639137325}}
{"type":"message","id":"26cae2fd","parentId":"3da27ea0","timestamp":"2026-03-27T19:19:01.705Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I need to search for latest news on relevant industries. Let me search for multiple topics related to 道简网络's business:\n1. 企业数字化转型\n2. 智能安防\n3. 网络系统集成\n4. IT运维服务\n\nLet me run searches for these topics.","thinkingSignature":"9f0c047193a0ddd131f61de3e17fde8435ea3f098db345748e042af35371b9a6"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_kox9xf4mx5j9_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"企业数字化转型 2026 最新政策趋势\" --output json 2>/dev/null | head -200","timeout":30}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_kox9xf4mx5j9_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"智能安防行业动态 2026\" --output json 2>/dev/null | head -200","timeout":30}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_kox9xf4mx5j9_3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"网络系统集成 IT运维服务 2026 最新动态\" --output json 2>/dev/null | head -200","timeout":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1534,"output":245,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45760,"cost":{"input":0.00046019999999999996,"output":0.000294,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00207363}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774639137328}}
